fulltitle: Anthony Braxton interviewed by Gerry Hemingway (2013)
tags: Association For The Advancement Of Creative Musicians (Nonprofit Organization)
title: Anthony Braxton interviewed by Gerry Hemingway (2013)
description: Jazz'nMore Magazine invited me to interview Anthony Braxton prior to our trio performance at the 2013 Willisau Festival with Taylor Ho Bynum. A portion of the interview was published (translated into German) by Jazz'n'More in the May/June Issue in 2014. This is the complete Interview.
